<span id="bedrock"></span>{{term|term='''[[bedrock]]'''}}
{{defn|defn=The solid rock in the Earth's {{gli|crust}} that underlies all soil or other loose material; the rock material that breaks down eventually to form soil.<ref name="IIP 2008"/>}}

<span id="bight"></span>{{term|term='''[[bight (geography)|bight]]'''}}
