<span id="body of water"></span>{{term|term='''[[body of water]]'''}}
{{defn|defn=Any significant accumulation of water, either natural or artificial, on the surface of the Earth. Bodies of water may hold or contain water, as with {{gli|lake|lakes}} and {{gli|ocean|oceans}}, or they may collect and move water from one place to another, as with {{gli|river|rivers}}, {{gli|stream|streams}}, and other {{gli|waterway|waterways}}.}}

