{{defn|defn=A stable community of people formed on the basis of a common geographic territory, language, economy, ethnicity, or psychological make-up as manifested in a common {{gli|culture}}.}}

<span id="national mapping agency"></span>{{term|term='''[[national mapping agency]]'''}}
