'''Primary direction''' is a term in [[astronomy]] for the reference [[meridian (astronomy)|meridian]] used in a [[celestial coordinate system]] for that system's [[longitude]].

==See also==
* [[Celestial coordinate system]]
* [[Geographic coordinate system]]

